This is a common topic in multiple areas of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and decision support systems (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the use of Markov processes, which is a common topic in the subfield of multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Finally, the paper discusses the concept of entropy production, which is a topic in statistical inference (cs.SI).
